== /harm ==

=== Basics ===

//Harms a player.//

**Usage:** /harm [player] [damage]

**Permission Nodes**
 * rcmds.harm
 * rcmds.exempt.harm

=== In Depth ===

{{{/harm}}} deals damage of the amount {{{[damage]}}} to {{{[player]}}}. {{{[damage]}}} is a value between one and
twenty half-hearts.

This command supports [[../name-completion.html|online name-completion]].

=== Examples ===

{{{/harm Notch 10}}} - Damages {{{Notch}}} for {{{10}}} half-hearts (5 hearts).